@startuml SSD
autonumber

actor "User" as User
participant "System" as System
actor "Weather API" as API

activate User
User -> System : requests weather info
activate System

System -> System : checks location permissions
System -> System : retrieves current location

System -> API : requests weather data with coordinates
activate API
API --> System : returns weather data
deactivate API

System --> User : displays current weather info
deactivate System
deactivate User
@enduml